Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for treating us to breakfast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We are country people \Nso our food is not fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad to see you've rested well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't slept so well through the night \Nin a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a great room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay as long as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, thanks but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have rooms to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are not in a hurry, \Ndo stay with us for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really generous in such hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know not about other places, \Nbut our village has nothing but peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not rich, \Nbut we do not need for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We are able to live thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,all thanks to the blessings from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd been trying to think of a way \Nto have him let us stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined he'd come out \Nand invite us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let the demons go free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That huge one might come \Nstraight for you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out to talk with the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious about the nun \Nand the burnt-out temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will watch Sabame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well don't do anything crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That old guy might just be brainwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks creepy, \Nbut don't judge a book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,悪ぃなぁ！朝メシまでご馳走んなっちまって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:36.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大したもてなしもできぬが、
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:38.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よく休めたようで何よりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:49.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お…おかげさまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:54.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,久しぶりに朝までぐーっすり眠れたぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:57.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なかなかいいな、この部屋。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,静かだし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:02.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,好きなだけ泊まってくれてかまわんぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:06.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え…？それは…ありがたいけどよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,部屋も余っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急ぐ旅でないのなら、ゆるりとしていくが良い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:17.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ。このご時世に太っ腹だなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お…おかわり、いい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:30.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うむ。他がどうだか知らぬが、ここは静かなことだけが取り柄の山里。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:35.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,豊かとも言えぬが、決して困ってもおらぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:36.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ、どうも！へへっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我らがこうして暮らしてゆけるのも、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:43.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すべて天の恵みと思うておる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:52.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたら居座れるかって考えてたのによぉ、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:57.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まさかあちら様からお誘いがあるとは思わなかったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:01.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神は…逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:08.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今度は初めからでっかいやつが襲ってくるかもよ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…それじゃ、おいらは里で話を聞いてくらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,尼さんと焼けた寺のことも気になるし。さ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:23.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきは？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鯖目を見張る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっか、無茶はすんなよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:32.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのおっさん、操られてるだけかもしれないし…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:37.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見た目は不気味だけど、人は見かけによらねぇって言うしな！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices \Nin the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light \Nin the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,#15 The story of the scene from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Hah! Take that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks for taking your time out \Nto help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's nothing. What are neighbors for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, watch it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get through winter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You all must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a break and have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's like any other village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cool tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, who's that kid over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, want some rice cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Me? \N-They're really tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, you're Lord Sabame's guest then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's really nice \Nfor letting a stranger like me stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. This looks so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Sabame puts this village \Nbefore everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We are able to live like this in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to Lord Sabame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a really great guy, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you address him like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I saw a burnt-out temple \Non my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Must get some more work done \Nwhile the sun is still high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, but Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, off we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my favorite place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a full view of the village \Nfrom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A grand storehouse in the woods \Naway from the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So fishy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's hidden treasure in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's guarding it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, just another rice storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This sure is a hard-working village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a full belly,  \N your heart will be calm and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping true to your ambition  \N when it could mean life or death...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that isn't something just anyone can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But they've really saved up a lot. \NWay too much for me to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? A hidden trapdoor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see a thing without a torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow... What the heck was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to protect the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My ancestors protected this land \Nfor generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born and raised here. \NI became the lord, and here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know not of any other places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As a traveler, you may not understand \Nwhat that's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This village is my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, \NI will protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here to kill \Nthe ghouls that live here, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right. \N-I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They, too, are my people. \NI must protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the heck! Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta let bro know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find a light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our village was in \Nthe clutches of hell, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The samurai who escaped wars  \N and became brigands
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,came and raided our peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The fields were left unattended  \N and ravaged by wild beasts and insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My people were hungry,  \N and stole from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was amidst such hell \Nthat I encountered "them".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is our destiny \Nto live on in this land,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I must protect the land and its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't care that they were ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ready to give up my soul if \Nit meant my people could escape this hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The ghouls ate the brigands \Nand killed the beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept their promise,  \N and our village prospered again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I welcomed "her" into my home  \N as my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you kill ghouls?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it, I'm not dying here \Nto be eaten by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care \Nwhat you're trying to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And get it all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-You saved me... \N-Dororo is kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I save Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the kids escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be fed to Maimai-onba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the village. No hard feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For the village? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind, Dororo. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry. We must hurry  \N or Maimai-onba's children will awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A vagabond like you \Nwould never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They've finally awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You will fill their empty stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The same... You are the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen bro, it was the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:17:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They killed the nun and the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The village, it's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was pushed down a trapdoor \Nin a storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then those huge bugs came at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They almost ate me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that big baby thing saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That baby ghost, it was the murdered kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the oil too.  \N The oil used to burn down the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it. It smelled the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure they couldn't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Sabame, all the village's rice \Nhas been burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-We won't last through the winter. \N-Lord Sabame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-What should we do? \N-How will we survive this winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't there still a stock of rice \Nat your house, Ishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your home hasn't burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands off. That's my rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to hog it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabame, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Lord Sabame's guest \Nstarted the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby ghoul said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole village...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, did we do the wrong thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened because we came, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you defeat a few demons  \N here and there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it won't change the world at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All you think about is killing the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll just make you one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you not perceive distance \Nwith just one eye yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish bro would listen to me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dororo. Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, come on. \NI've been looking everywhere for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Still a midget, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da. Now show me the other half \Nthat you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:23.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ふーんげふーんげぇ！ふーんだ！ぽーんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:28.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉーい！すまねぇなぁみんな忙しいときによぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:32.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいってことよ！お互い様さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:33.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おわったた！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お…おいおい！気ぃ付けてよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:36.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったくだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これで今年も冬を越せるねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほんにありがたいねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうひと働き頑張っぺ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やるべやるべ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みんな、ご苦労さん。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひと休みして、お湯でもあがれや
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ…普通の村だよな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イカすやぐらだねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ばっちゃ！知らない子だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉーい！おだんごあるよぉー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:32.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん…？おいら？\Nおだんご！おいしいよー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:42.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうかい…あんた鯖目様のお客さんかい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:47.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ。おいらみたいなよそ者を泊めてくれるなんてさぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホントありがたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん。おだんご
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:56.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい。どうじょ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまねぇな。おぉうまそうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:10.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鯖目様はなぁ、いつでもこの里のことを一番に考えてくださるんじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わしらがこうして暮らしてゆけるのも、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すべて鯖目様のおかげなんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:20.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へぇー、偉いんだなあのおっさん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:23.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こら！おっさんとは何じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…いや、ごめん。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:32.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういえばさ、この村に来る途中に焼けた寺を見たんだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ばあちゃん知ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さ、行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:45.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁーて、お天道さんが高いうちに、もうひと仕事やっちまわねえとな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えぇー？でもばっちゃまー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さ、行くんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも、あたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私はこの場所が好きでな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,里を見渡せる、この場所がな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怪しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:31.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村のはずれの林ん中に、こんな立派な蔵があるなんて。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:34.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,んー、怪しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:44.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱり怪しい。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんか訳ありかなー。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,秘密のお宝隠してたりして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そして、無用心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよ…ただの米蔵じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやぁ、さすが働き者の村だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:11.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,腹いっぱい食えれば、心も穏やかになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:16.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食うや食わずの身の上でそれでも志を貫けるのなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:19.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほんの一握りだけだからねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:24.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しかしよく溜め込んだよな。おいらのふところには大きすぎるや
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わぁっ！ってぇ…あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:34.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これって…秘密の扉かな？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あー…こりゃ明かりがないとなんも見えないなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そりゃあそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:49.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ってぇ…！何しやがんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すまねぇなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,里を守るためなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:04.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここは我が祖先が代々守ってきた土地でな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:08.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここで生まれ、ここで育ち、領主になって今がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他の場所を私は知らぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:19.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,旅人のそなたには及びもつかぬことやも知れぬがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,の里が私のすべてよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何があろうと私はこの土地を守り抜く。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:32.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなた…この土地に住まうあやかしを討ちに来たのであろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ\N討たせはせぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやつらも私が守らねばならぬ民なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:47.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！ふざけんな！出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出せってばぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハァ…なんだよあいつら…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつらやばいよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,早くあにきに知らせなきゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんか明かりんなるもん見つけなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいおい、これって…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきぃ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:19.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このご時世だ。我が里も地獄の中にあった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:24.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いくさ場から逃げ落ちて野伏せりとなった者どもが、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦うことを知らぬ里を襲う
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:32.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,守り手を失った田畑は獣や虫に犯されて…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,飢えを生み、民たちは互いに奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:43.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな地獄で私は出会ったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやつらに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:53.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この地にて我らが生きることを許されるならば、
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必ずこの地を守り抜かん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まやかしでも構わぬと思うた。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:08.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が民がこの地獄から抜け出せるのなら、\N私の心など売り渡しても良いと思うた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:14.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あやつらは野伏せりを喰らい\N獣を殺し
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:19.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私との約定を守り、里は蘇った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:25.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そして…私はあやつを妻として迎えたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひとつ聞きたい。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:31.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そなたはなぜあやかしを斬るのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くそっ！お前らに喰われてたまるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わっ！ってぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう…ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うわ…やべぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:08.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんで…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前が何を守ろうと関係ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺は鬼神を…斬る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,斬って…取り戻す。全部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:33.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前…おいらのこと\Nどろろ優しくしてくれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから助けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,子供らを逃がすなー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:22.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たちはマイマイオンバ様のエサになるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:26.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,里のみんなのためだ…悪く思うでねぇぞ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなのってあるかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,里のため…そんなの…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろは優しいのね。ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:42.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,泣かないで。急がないとマイマイオンバの子が目覚めてしまうわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私についてきて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,所詮、流れ者にはわかるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ようやくこの子らも目覚めた。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:13.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様にはこの子らのエサになってもらおう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:37.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,同じ…お前も同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:15:58.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,邪魔だぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！聞いとくれよ！この村のやつらだったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:17:00.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,の尼さんと子供たち、みんなあいつらにやられたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:04.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ！燃えてる！村のほう…そうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,米蔵で下に落とされて...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしたら、あの虫が襲ってきて、
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらは食われそうだったんだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのでかい赤ん坊みたいなあやかしに助けられて。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:16.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でね…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:20.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのあやかしは、殺された子供達で！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…聞いてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:23.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:29.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,油…油も見つけたんだ。寺を燃やした油だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:32.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,同じ匂いがしたから間違いねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらが使えないようにしといたけどな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:45.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鯖目様…里の蓄えが全部…全部燃えちまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:48.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これじゃあ、冬を越せねぇぞ！\N鯖目様！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうすりゃあいんですかぁ！\Nこの冬、俺たちどうすんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:57.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういやぁ、医師のとこにゃあまだ納めてねぇ\N稲がひと山あったんじゃねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,医師の家ゃ燃えてねぇぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！あれはおらの米だぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おめぇ！ひとり占めする気か！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい鯖目！どうにかしろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,火ぃ点けたのは鯖目様の火手らしいぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,湖に？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん…子供のあやかしがそう言ってたけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:20.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだい…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この村…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんで…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでこんなんなっちゃうんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:32.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…おいら、おいらたちどうすればよかったのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:36.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらたちが来たから、この村はこんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:37.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,関係ない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神の何匹か斬ったところで、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,世の中なんにも変わりゃしないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきは鬼神を殺せばそれでいいんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,答えてくれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんなのやっぱおかしいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:57.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これじゃあにきも同じんなっちまう…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:16.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ片方の目では、間合いがつかめませぬか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…もう一度だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺には…関係ない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:40.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…どろろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:50.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…もうちょっとおいらの話聞いてくれたっていいじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきのバカ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:03.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よぉ。どろろ。久しぶりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イタチか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:09.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つれないなぁ。ずいぶん探したんだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:14.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前のことヒヒハハッハ…相変わらずチビだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:15.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うるせぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:21.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハハ。じゃーん！見せてもらうぜ？お前が持ってる残りの半分をよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love  \N this accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world  \N on our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.88,0:23:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Maimai-onba"
